To incorporate `function printPdf()` into your existing code, keep the following in mind:

+ UiApp has been [deprecated][1] and thus,

```lang:js
    var app = UiApp.createApplication().setWidth(300).setHeight(100);
    app.setTitle(&#39;Your Print Preview is Ready&#39;);
